channel.title: [317 Delta] Command ::jail help! Teleporting! [Bluur]
channel.description:
Hello everyone. I recently changed up the jail area, so i changed the coordinates in the command to the new jail. So whenever i do ::jail (player name) they get teleported to the new jail i created. But whenever they click anything, in the new jail, they teleport to the old jail?
Help. Thanks.
